➜【星连文学社】苏坛：《观音柳》
http://www.sohu.com/a/411448732_100115135	43595
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200804/8821f578dd854cbea187ce6eb04424f4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《观音柳》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远去了，老屋门前的那棵观音柳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逝去了，建在废城墙土基上的老屋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老岳母喜欢打理着废弃护城河里的菜地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老岳父照看好护城河边的观音柳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我站立在观音柳下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>观看着柔弱细长的枝条随风拂动</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>默默地祈祷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这插入观音菩萨净瓶中的观音柳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>法力无边，度一切苦厄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">观音柳走出了我的视界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却走不出我的心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我和它相处了十六年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那里有一家人深深的爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200804/3ada26c6a9f64e2a87b22a96344b3daa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
